### Recommend Service — REST Client test file
### Requires VS Code extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
###
### Prerequisites:
###   1. docker compose -f infra/docker-compose.yml up -d neo4j redis rabbitmq
###   2. pnpm nx run recommend-service:install
###   3. pnpm nx run recommend-service:serve
###
### Auth: Gateway đã validate JWT và forward X-User-Id — service tin tưởng header này trực tiếp.
### Endpoint /similar/{trackId} là public, không cần X-User-Id.

@baseUrl  = http://localhost:8000
@userId   = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@userId2  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@trackId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
@trackId2 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011

###
### ─── RECOMMENDATIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [1] Lấy recommendations — mặc định (limit=20)
### Cold-start nếu user chưa có lịch sử nghe: trả popular-fallback
### Có lịch sử: trả collaborative-filtering-v2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [2] Recommendations với limit tùy chỉnh
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?limit=5
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [3] Recommendations lọc theo genre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?genre=POP
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [4] Recommendations lọc genre + giới hạn số lượng
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?genre=ELECTRONIC&limit=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [5] Recommendations với seed=genre (boost genre preferred)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?seed=genre
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [6] Limit = 1 (min)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?limit=1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [7] Limit = 100 (max)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?limit=100
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [8] Limit vượt max (101) → 422 Unprocessable Entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?limit=101
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [9] Limit = 0 → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations?limit=0
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [10] Thiếu X-User-Id → 422 Unprocessable Entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations

###

### [11] User khác — kiểm tra cache độc lập
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}

###
### ─── DISCOVER WEEKLY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [12] Lấy Discover Weekly playlist (cache 7 ngày)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/discover-weekly
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [13] Discover Weekly — user khác
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/discover-weekly
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}

###

### [14] Thiếu X-User-Id → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/discover-weekly

###
### ─── SIMILAR TRACKS (PUBLIC) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [15] Similar tracks — public, không cần X-User-Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId}}

###

### [16] Similar tracks — với limit tùy chỉnh
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId}}?limit=5

###

### [17] Similar tracks — limit = 1 (min)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId}}?limit=1

###

### [18] Similar tracks — limit = 50 (max)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId}}?limit=50

###

### [19] Similar tracks — limit vượt max (51) → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId}}?limit=51

###

### [20] Similar tracks — trackId khác
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/{{trackId2}}

###

### [21] Similar tracks — trackId không tồn tại trong graph → 200 items=[]
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/similar/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099

###
### ─── RADIO MODE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [22] Radio từ seed track — mặc định 25 tracks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [23] Radio — limit tùy chỉnh
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId}}?limit=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [24] Radio — limit = 1 (min)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId}}?limit=1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [25] Radio — limit = 50 (max)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId}}?limit=50
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [26] Radio — seed track khác
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId2}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [27] Radio — thiếu X-User-Id → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/radio/{{trackId}}

###
### ─── FEEDBACK ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [28] Feedback LIKE — tạo SAVED edge trong Neo4j, invalidate cache
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "LIKE"
}

###

### [29] Feedback DISLIKE — tạo DISLIKED edge, exclude khỏi future recs
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "DISLIKE"
}

###

### [30] Feedback SKIP — no-op trong Neo4j
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "SKIP"
}

###

### [31] Feedback SAVE_TO_PLAYLIST — tạo SAVED edge
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "SAVE_TO_PLAYLIST",
  "context": "playlist-abc"
}

###

### [32] Feedback — action không hợp lệ → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "INVALID_ACTION"
}

###

### [33] Feedback — thiếu trackId → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "LIKE"
}

###

### [34] Feedback — thiếu X-User-Id → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}",
  "action": "LIKE"
}

###
### ─── TASTE PROFILE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [35] Lấy taste profile — genreWeights + topArtists + profileStrength
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [36] Taste profile — user mới, chưa có lịch sử nghe → profile rỗng
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}

###

### [37] Taste profile — thiếu X-User-Id → 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile

###
### ─── TASTE PROFILE REFRESH ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### [38] Refresh taste profile — invalidate Redis cache recs:{userId} + discover-weekly:{userId}
### → 202 Accepted
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile/refresh
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [39] Refresh → sau đó lấy lại recommendations (cache đã bị xoá → Neo4j query)
# Bước 1: gọi refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile/refresh
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### [40] Refresh — thiếu X-User-Id → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/taste-profile/refresh

